Package: KRIG
Type: Package
Title: Kriging
Version: 0.1.0
Encoding: UTF-8
Date: 2017-10-17
Author: Pedro Guarderas
Maintainer: Pedro Guarderas <pedro.felipe.guarderas@gmail.com>
Description: Computes simple, ordinary and universal kriging, also computes simple, ordinary and 
    universal cokriging. In addition, includes functions for Sensitivity analysis based in the 
    approximation, inside Reproducing Kernel Hilbert spaces, of Sobol indices.
License: LGPL-3
URL: https://github.com/pedroguarderas/KRIG
